data.description: OPEN HOUSE SUN 9/24 12-2pm. This stunning MOVE-IN READY 4 bed/2.5 bath home is on one of the most desirable lots nestled in the beautiful Longview Highlands community in Pickerington. HUGE backyard that overlooks a serene view of lush greens and mature trees. Steps away from a neighborhood playground and located near Pickerington Ponds Metro Park. With over 2,300 sqft, the first floor features an open layout of the kitchen, dining, and living room for easy entertaining, as well as a flex space for an office/den or play room. Gorgeous kitchen w/ granite countertops, high-end SS appliances, & walk-in pantry. SPACIOUS primary-suite, 3 large bedrooms, 2nd floor laundry, walk-in closets + extra storage room. FULL basement that is plumbed and ready to be finished!
